<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1893-05-17T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1893-05-17T00:00:00-05:00" n="508" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d508">
                        <head><hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Gresham</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">White</persName>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1893-05-17"><hi rend="italic">May 17,
                                1893</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>Representations made here that Russian Government is about to enforce
                            edict against Jews, which will result in a large emigration of destitute
                            people of that class to the United States.</p>
                        <p>If there is foundation for what we hear, you will please ascertain and
                            report as speedily as possible the terms of the edict and its probable
                            effect.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Gresham.</hi></signed></closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>